snippet: Stan Wawrinka edged out Cypriot Marcos Baghdatis in a nerve-jangling, near-30 minute tiebreak to secure the Dubai Duty Free Championship with a 6-4 7-6(13) triumph on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Stan Wawrinka edged out Cypriot Marcos Baghdatis in a nerve-jangling, near-30 minute tiebreak to secure the Dubai Duty Free Championship with a 6-4 7-6(13) triumph on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Wins Dubai Title After Marathon Tiebreak
headline.main: Wawrinka Wins Dubai Title After Marathon Tiebreak
